-- Bahrain Seeks Suspects After 5 Tons of Explosive Materials Found
-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 2012-06-28T14:05:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/bahrain-seeks-suspects-after-5-tons-of-explosive-materials-found.html
Bahraini police are seeking three
people suspected of assembling home-made bombs after 5 tons of
explosive materials were uncovered during raids, the Information
Affairs Authority said.  “The explosives were designed to cause severe injury, a
high death toll, serious destruction to property, and fear in
the minds of the public,” Major-General Tariq al-Hassan, chief
of public security, said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wael Mahdi in Manama at 
 wmahdi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
